Project goals:
  PHP Crawler is a simple website search for small-to-middle website.
  The only requrements is PHP and MySQL, no shell access required.

Key features: 
+ Easy install. Unpack, crawl and enjoy your website search.
+ indexer can be started from shell or just by accessing a web page
+ Configurable crawl depth
+ No daemons, apache modules or additional software required
+ Customizable search page
+ Crawler prints page size (text part only)

